nme.com/news/music/oasis-tour-internation-2025-reunion-cities-america-asia-australia-3797221"><em>NME</em>独家透露 Oasis 将在即将到来的 2025 年重聚巡演中演出的城市几天后，有关北美和墨西哥演出的详细信息公布了。</a></p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">上个月宣布他们期待已久的重聚</a>并确认<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-respond-to-glastonbury-2025-rumours-and-the-chances-of-other-festivals-3788269">明年不会参加任何音乐节</a>之后，乐队开始向歌迷暗示，他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-plans-underway-for-2025-shows-outside-of-europe-3787647">还计划在世界各地举行其他重要的演出</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="“我仍然可以鼓起摇滚脾气”：利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 凯旋归来" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/snlgEbG6Z14?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>接近巡演的消息人士告诉<em>NME</em> ，乐队很快将宣布在首尔、东京、悉尼、墨尔本、圣保罗、圣地亚哥和布宜诺斯艾利斯举行更多国际演出。</p><p>他们还告诉<em>《NME》</em> ，除了现已确定在芝加哥、新泽西、洛杉矶、墨西哥城和多伦多举行的日期外，还计划在美国举办另一场演出，据报道定于马萨诸塞州波士顿举行。</p><p>有关其他演出的确切场地、日期和门票销售详情的更多详细信息将很快公布。</p><p>英国演出的门票销售引发了争议，因为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-2025-fans-frustrated-as-theyre-held-in-long-queues-on-ticketmaster-3789320">粉丝们经历了长时间的排队和技术困难</a>，并且 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-fans-react-to-ticketmasters-dynamic-pricing-3789361">由于“动态”的激增定价而导致大量门票以虚高的价格出售</a>。</p><p>为了回应这种强烈反对，绿洲“向弥补这一局面迈出了一小步”，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-wembley-stadium-extra-reunion-dates-tickets-invite-only-no-surge-pricing-3790552">宣布了两个额外的温布利球场日期</a>，这些日期通过仅限邀请的投票分批出售。他们还表示，他们自己<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-band-say-they-at-no-time-had-any-awareness-that-dynamic-pricing-was-going-to-be-used-3790679">“从来没有意识到将使用动态定价”</a> 。</p><p>虽然 Cage The Elephant 已被宣布为北美和墨西哥演出的支持表演， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/oasis-reunion-line-up-band-members-guide-3788552">但人们仍然猜测谁将加入英伦流行音乐传奇人物的英国演出</a>。</p><p>到目前为止，粉丝们一直在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wholl-be-supporting-oasis-on-their-reunion-tour-fans-and-artists-share-theories-and-requests-3787727">讨论潜在的支持行为</a>——其中提到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blossoms-respond-to-oasis-reunion-tour-support-rumours-3793918">Blossoms</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kasabian">Kasabian</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-responds-to-rumours-of-richard-ashcroft-supporting-oasis-on-reunion-tour-3793657">Richard Ashcroft</a>等人。本月早些时候，有<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-reportedly-seeking-established-acts-to-support-oasis-on-reunion-tour-3793095">报道称 Liam 正在寻找“知名乐队”在 2025 年为 Oasis 开场</a>，但目前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/it-doesnt-look-like-suede-will-be-supporting-oasis-on-their-reunion-tour-3795466">看来不太可能是 Suede</a>或<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-on-why-they-couldnt-really-give-a-shit-about-the-oasis-reunion-3793122">Fontaines DC，因为主唱在网上对这两个乐队进行了猛烈抨击</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3798256" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3798256" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3798256" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Cage-The-Elephant@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Cage The Elephant 的马特·舒尔茨 (Matt Shultz) 将于 2024 年演出" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Cage-The-Elephant@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Cage-The-Elephant@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Cage-The-Elephant@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Cage-The-Elephant@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Cage-The-Elephant@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Cage-The-Elephant@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3798256" class="wp-caption-text"> Cage The Elephant 乐队的马特·舒尔茨 (Matt Shultz) 将于 2024 年演出。图片来源：Gary Miller/WireImage/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>关于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-2025-reunion-tour-more-dates-rumoured-to-be-added-with-bonehead-reportedly-in-band-line-up-3788098">谁将与利亚姆和诺埃尔一起加入重新组合的绿洲阵容，</a>也存在争议。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-2025-reunion-tour-more-dates-rumoured-to-be-added-with-bonehead-reportedly-in-band-line-up-3788098">据报道，原吉他手 Paul &#39;Bonehead&#39; Arthurs 将参加巡演，</a>其他传闻成员包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gem-archer-is-looking-very-likely-to-join-oasis-line-up-for-their-2025-reunion-tour-3789719">吉他手 Gem Archer</a>和贝斯手 Andy Bell。鼓手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/alan-white-teases-joining-oasis-reunion-line-up-3789548">艾伦·怀特也在他的社交媒体上引发了谣言</a>，但<em>NME</em>相信他不会出现在阵容中。利亚姆此后开玩笑说， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-says-there-could-be-a-few-new-faces-in-oasis-reunion-tour-band-3795146">该阵容可能会有“一些新面孔</a>”。</p><p>即将到来的重聚演出将是自<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-380-1313832">2009 年 Oasis 分裂</a>以来兄弟俩首次一起演出。两人在巴黎塞纳河音乐节上发生“争吵”后发生了争执，就在他们亮相头条新闻的几个小时前。</p><p>最近，利亚姆在温布利体育场举行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-liam-gallagher-perform-oasis-classics-ahead-of-anthony-joshua-vs-daniel-dubois-boxing-match-at-wembley-stadium-3795901">安东尼·约书亚 (Anthony Joshua) 对阵丹尼尔·杜波依斯 (Daniel Dubois) 拳击比赛之前表演了绿洲经典</a>曲目，继他在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/liam-gallagher-reading-festival-2024-review-setlist-photos-oasis-reunion-noel-3787153#:~:text=Recommended,%E2%80%9CDon't%20be%20shy.">雷丁 2024 年的头条新闻</a>之后。</p><p>后来，他因猛烈抨击<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-hits-back-at-shitc-critics-who-mocked-his-vocals-at-wembley-stadium-you-aint-real-fans-youre-just-imposters-3795959">那些在网上抱怨他歌声的“SHITC**T”评论家而登上</a>头条，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-says-goodbye-to-live-band-at-last-scheduled-solo-show-in-malta-3796207">在马耳他举行最后一次个人演出时告别了他的乐队。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-2025-reunion-tour-dates-in-north-america-and-mexico-buy-tickets-3798246">Oasis 宣布 2025 年北美和墨西哥重聚巡演日期的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
学术研究表明，玩“PowerWash Simulator”对你有好处https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/playing-powerwash-simulator-is-good-for-you-says-academic-study-3798261?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=playing-powerwash-simulator-对你有好处说学术学习Ali ShutlerMon, 30 Sep 2024 11:54:31 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsNintendo SwitchPCPlayStation 5Xbox Series X/S https://www.nme.com/?p=3798261 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/PowerWash-Simulator.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="PowerWash 模拟器屏幕截图" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/PowerWash-Simulator.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/PowerWash-Simulator-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/PowerWash-Simulator-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/PowerWash-Simulator-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/PowerWash-Simulator-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/PowerWash-Simulator-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该报告由牛津大学和牛津互联网研究所牵头</p><p>学术研究首先发表在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/playing-powerwash-simulator-is-good-for-you-says-academic-study-3798261">，称玩“PowerWash Simulator”对你有好处</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/PowerWash-Simulator.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="PowerWash 模拟器屏幕截图" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/PowerWash-Simulator.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/PowerWash-Simulator-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/PowerWash-Simulator-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/PowerWash-Simulator-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/PowerWash-Simulator-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/PowerWash-Simulator-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一项新的学术研究证明，玩<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/powerwash-simulator">PowerWash Simulator</a></em>对您有好处。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/powerwash-simulator-is-an-inexplicably-brilliant-game-about-cleaning-up-the-neighbourhood-3141620">“PowerWash Simulator”是一款关于清理社区的精彩游戏</a></strong></li></ul><p><em>PowerWash Simulator</em>于 2022 年发布，鼓励玩家“用高压水的舒缓声音冲走你的忧虑。启动你的电动洗衣机，把你能找到的每一粒污垢和污垢都吹掉，所有这一切都可以通过电动清洗来获得闪闪发光的表面简单的满足感。”</p><p>同年，FuturLabs 发布了该游戏的特殊“ <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/1290000/view/3409807423269852954?l=english" target="_blank" rel="noopener">教育</a>”版本，以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/powerwash-simulator-partners-with-oxford-university-to-research-gaming-and-mental-health-3293740">帮助牛津大学和牛津互联网研究所正在进行的一项研究</a>，该研究“以 PowerWash Simulator 玩家的福祉为中心，同时旨在提供对游戏和心理健康的更广泛讨论的见解。”</p><p>现在牛津研究的<a href="https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.1145/3659464" target="_blank" rel="noopener">结果</a>已经公布，72% 的玩家表示在玩 PowerWash Simulator 后情绪有所提升。 FuturLab 表示：“这种变化与阅读、购物或听音乐等其他休闲活动中的变化相当。”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">结果在<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f4a6.png" alt="💦" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p>不久前，我们与牛津大学合作研究玩电子游戏对玩家心理健康的影响。感谢所有参与的人<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f499.png" alt="💙" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p>要阅读更多内容，请点击此链接<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2b07.png" alt="⬇" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/XN0H7sYkEl">https://t.co/XN0H7sYkEl</a> <a href="https://t.co/w1w0As729J">pic.twitter.com/w1w0As729J</a></p><p> - PowerWash 模拟器 (@PowerWashSim) <a href="https://twitter.com/PowerWashSim/status/1839303590273495358?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 9 月 26 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>这项研究继续进行，该研究涵盖了来自 39 个国家的超过 8,695 名玩家。</p><p>在谈到这项研究时，蒂尔堡大学助理教授兼牛津互联网研究所副研究员 Matti Vuorre 表示：“目前，人们对视频游戏玩家情绪的短期变化知之甚少。游戏玩法研究经常依赖于人工刺激，由学术研究人员创建或修改的游戏通常在实验室环境而不是自然环境中进行。相反，我们想知道自然环境中的真实游戏如何在短时间内预测玩家的情绪。”</p><p>今年早些时候，日本科学家主导的一份报告发现， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/new-study-proves-playing-video-games-is-good-for-you-3785551">玩电子游戏可以缓解压力并改善心理健康，但前提是使用受到限制，</a>而<em>PowerWash Simulator</em>的下一次更新将于 10 月 10 日发布，届时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/you-can-now-play-as-shrek-in-powerwash-simulator-3788108">玩家将能够清洁爬上史莱克的沼泽。</a></p><p>其他消息方面，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/kojima-productions">小岛秀夫</a>已确认<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/death-stranding-2">《死亡搁浅 2》</a></em>的发售日期，但他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/death-stranding-2-2025-release-date-new-footage-3798218">暂时保密。</a></p><p>学术研究首先发表在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/playing-powerwash-simulator-is-good-for-you-says-academic-study-3798261">，称玩“PowerWash Simulator”对你有好处</a>。</p> ;
